**LogEchoSplice**  
**Description:**  
Splices together similar log segments to reveal echoed sequences and recurring block structures.

```markdown
# LogEchoSplice - Log Segment Repetition Detector

LogEchoSplice finds near-identical log segments repeated across time or components to reveal faulty patterns.

## Features
- Log splice mapping  
- Echo chain analysis  
- Lightweight CLI tool

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/LogEchoSplice.git
cd LogEchoSplice
python analyze.py
